        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"171497\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>2002 is an underrated Bordeaux vintage. Not as underrated or as good as 2001, but some really good wines were made.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I like 2001 particularly the Right Bank. But my sleeper vintage from this era is 2004, which reminds me a lot of 1979.</p>",
